dcterms:creator: Alex Krizhevsky
dcterms:description: A dataset containing 60,000 32x32 color images in 10 different classes, with 6,000 images per class. It is commonly used for training machine learning models in computer vision.
dcterms:title: CIFAR-10

dcterms:creator: Alex Krizhevsky
dcterms:description: A dataset containing 60,000 32x32 color images in 100 different classes, with 600 images per class. It is used for evaluating machine learning models in fine-grained image classification tasks.
dcterms:title: CIFAR-100
